source.name: CTA - Bus Turnarounds - Shapefile
source.description:
Point data representing locations of all bus turnarounds that are not located at Rail Stations. To view or use these files, compression software and special GIS software, such as ESRI ArcGIS is required.                                                                                          
Projected Coordinate System:	NAD_1983_StatePlane_Illinois_East_FIPS_1201_Feet
